{"title":"Bootstrap组件","date":"2019-05-03T08:48:51.000Z","link":"post/demo-2-element","tags":["Bootstrap","css","前端","组件"],"updated":"2019-05-03T11:44:50.000Z","content":"<h1 id=\"组件\">组件<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#组件\"></a></h1><h4 id=\"文本警报\">文本警报<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#文本警报\"></a></h4><p>通过增加以下class属性可以更改文本属性</p>\n<div class=\"article-bounded\"><div class=\"article-table\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>alert-primary</th>\n<th>alert-secondary</th>\n<th>alert-success</th>\n<th>alert-danger</th>\n<th>alert-warning</th>\n<th>alert-info</th>\n<th>alert-light</th>\n<th>alert-dark</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>主要-蓝</td>\n<td>二级-灰</td>\n<td>成功-绿</td>\n<td>危险-红</td>\n<td>警告-黄</td>\n<td>信息-天蓝</td>\n<td>灯光-白</td>\n<td>黑暗-黑灰</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;div class=\"alert alert-primary\" role=\"alert\"&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果文本中有链接可以增加以下更改颜色同步文本颜色</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">class=\"alert-link\"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>同样还可以在其他地方设置只需要使用表一的属性名即可</p>\n<h4 id=\"驳回关闭\">驳回关闭<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#驳回关闭\"></a></h4><p>我们可以在需要关闭的元素内部添加,记得引入js文件</p>\n<p>需要添加一个dismiss按键和<code>.alert-dismissible</code>类，他会在右侧添加删除按钮</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">//父级元素必须有.fade 和 .show</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div class=\"alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade show\" role=\"alert\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;button type=\"button\" class=\"close\" data-dismiss=\"alert\" aria-label=\"Close\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;span aria-hidden=\"true\"&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;/button&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"徽章\">徽章<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#徽章\"></a></h2><h4 id=\"标题徽章\">标题徽章<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#标题徽章\"></a></h4><p>在你需要变成标签徽章的标签里设置<code>badge badge-secondary</code>这个属性即可</p>\n<h4 id=\"按钮\">按钮<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#按钮\"></a></h4><p>请注意，根据屏幕阅读器和类似辅助技术的使用者的不同，徽章可能会令人困惑。虽然徽章的样式提供了关于其目的的视觉提示，但是这些用户将被简单地呈现徽章的内容。根据具体情况，这些徽章可能看起来像句子，链接或按钮末尾的随机附加单词或数字。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  Notifications &lt;span class=\"badge badge-light\"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/button&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"给标签徽章各种颜色\">给标签徽章各种颜色<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#给标签徽章各种颜色\"></a></h4><p>颜色与文本报错一样用途是改变背景颜色</p>\n<p>使用<code>.badge-pill</code>修饰符类可以使徽章更圆润</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge .badge-pill badge-primary\"&gt;Primary&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge badge-secondary\"&gt;Secondary&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge badge-success\"&gt;Success&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge badge-danger\"&gt;Danger&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge badge-warning\"&gt;Warning&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge badge-info\"&gt;Info&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge badge-light\"&gt;Light&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span class=\"badge badge-dark\"&gt;Dark&lt;/span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>同样我们链接也可以使用 使用元素<code>.badge-*</code>上的上下文类<em>可以</em><code>&lt;a&gt;</code>快速为悬停和焦点状态提供<em>可操作的</em>标记。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;a href=\"#\" class=\"badge badge-success\"&gt;Success&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"面包屑\">面包屑<a href=\"post/demo-2-element#面包屑\"></a></h4><p>和地址导航有点类似和它名字不相关哈哈哈</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;ol class=\"breadcrumb\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"&gt;&lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"&gt;&lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;Library&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;li class=\"breadcrumb-item active\" aria-current=\"page\"&gt;Data&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;/ol&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/nav&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Es6学习笔记：Set数据结构","link":"post/Es6之Set数据结构"},"next":{"title":"Bootstrap入门","link":"post/demo-1-grid"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/demo-2-element/","toc":[{"title":"组件","id":"组件","index":"1","children":[{"title":"徽章","id":"徽章","index":"1.1"}]}]}